nded destination.</p><h2 class=\"thHead\">Countermeasures</h2><p class=\"thBody\"><img src=\"images/symbol/x.gif\" />  <b>Suppress</b>: Arcana (trained only) DC 27 (standard action). <i>Requirement:</i> The character must be in the hazard\'s aura. <i>Success:</i> The hazard’s attack and aura cease to function until the end of the character’s next turn.<i> Failure (22 or lower):</i> The character takes 15 force damage.</p><p class=\"publishedIn\">Published in <a href=\"http://anonym.to/?http://www.wizards.com/default.asp?x=dnd/dutoc/203\" target=\"_new\">Dungeon Magazine 203</a>.</p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </form>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\n    if (document.all) {\r\n        if (document.documentMode != 9) {\r\n            var ar = document.getElementsByTagName(\'span\');\r\n            for (var i = 0; i < ar.length; i++ ) {\r\n                var c = ar[i].attributes[\'class\'].value;\r\n                if (c == \'milevel\')\r\n                    ar[i].style.top = \"-24px\";\r\n                else if (c == \'miright\')\r\n                    ar[i].style.top = \"-18px\";\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n</script>\r\n','');
